WEBVTT

00:02.103 --> 00:03.869
I loved you the
first moment I saw you.

00:03.971 --> 00:06.572
- Why in God's
name would I trade one
broke artist for another?

00:06.874 --> 00:08.073
Opium.

00:08.175 --> 00:09.575
- I want to
make you happy.

00:09.677 --> 00:11.777
I worship you, Fernande.

00:12.346 --> 00:13.846
Henri Matisse.

00:13.948 --> 00:15.748
No, this artist has
more than just talent.

00:15.850 --> 00:17.249
He has vision.

00:17.351 --> 00:20.352
He's bent all the rules,
and I want to smash them.

00:21.188 --> 00:22.254
- We
have done it, Pablo.

00:24.025 --> 00:25.090
- When the Autumn
Salon opens, you'll
both be sensations.

00:25.626 --> 00:27.292
- Matisse.
I'm not submitting it.

00:27.628 --> 00:28.727
- But why?

00:28.829 --> 00:30.062
- It's not good enough.

00:30.164 --> 00:31.964
- This is
exactly how you raised me.

00:32.066 --> 00:33.265
To stand up for myself.

00:33.367 --> 00:35.000
- I want you to
stay away from Picasso.

00:35.102 --> 00:38.037
- You're not actually
in love with him, are you?

00:38.472 --> 00:41.173
- My African
masks protect me against
all evil spirits.

00:42.510 --> 00:44.777
- We found her
wandering along the river,

00:45.646 --> 00:47.746
but there was no
evidence of an attack.

00:47.848 --> 00:49.548
Perhaps you should
take her to the hospital.

00:49.650 --> 00:52.184
I don't think
she's in her right mind.

00:52.520 --> 00:54.620
- You think
she doesn't mind because
she's such a free thinker,

00:54.722 --> 00:56.288
but she does mind, very much.

00:56.390 --> 00:58.624
I'm sorry, I thought
I could do things
your way, but I can't.

00:58.726 --> 01:02.027
I'm going to look after
myself, and I hope
you look after Dora.

01:03.164 --> 01:07.966
.

