49:20.692 --> 49:22.725
- The Mona Lisa.
Stolen from the Louvre.

49:22.827 --> 49:23.960
They'll accuse us!

49:24.062 --> 49:25.795
- Pablo Picasso?

49:25.897 --> 49:28.831
- If your work
doesn't give you trouble,
it won't be good.

49:29.500 --> 49:33.336
Francoise, where
could she have gone?

49:35.039 --> 49:37.940
- We have to rip
everything apart to create a
new kind of painting.

49:38.042 --> 49:39.909
- You are working
with Picasso aren't you?

49:40.011 --> 49:42.078
I cannot recommend this work.

